data.eml:eml: A revision of Strophurus taenicauda (Squamata, Diplodactylidae) with the description of two new subspecies from central Queensland and a southerly range extension

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Brown, Danny, Wilmer, Jessica Worthington, Macdonald, Stewart (2012): A revision of Strophurus taenicauda (Squamata, Diplodactylidae) with the description of two new subspecies from central Queensland and a southerly range extension. Zootaxa 3243: 1-28, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.215367
